    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are solid, the car shows visible signs of age including some minor door dings and fading paint on the roof. The interior is clean but has moderate wear on the driver's seat and some light staining on the carpets. It is a great option for someone needing a functional car who doesn't mind a few cosmetic imperfections.",
