    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a donor for parts. The engine is currently struggling to stay idle and will require a comprehensive mechanical overhaul to be roadworthy again. Body-wise, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several significant dents, while the interior shows heavy wear and tear. It is being sold strictly as-is, and I recommend a trailer for transport.",
