    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next road trip? I\u2019m selling my car, and it\u2019s in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been super dependable for me and still drives like a dream. It\u2019s been well-loved and is just waiting for a new owner to take it on some fun adventures. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
