    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and luxury. The exterior features a stunning Deep Midnight Blue finish that still holds a high-gloss luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the leading edge of the hood from standard highway use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort with premium charcoal leather upholstery; the driver\u2019s seat shows only light softening on the bolster, and the interior remains smoke-free and crisp. All onboard technology, including the navigation system and premium audio, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is sound, having followed a strict manufacturer-recommended service schedule with full records available. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are imperceptible. The alloy wheels show very minor curb contact on the rear passenger side, but they are wrapped in high-tread tires replaced just last season. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
